      <h1>Scale for shapes, aka glyphs.</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span8">
    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <pre><span class="functioncall"><a href='scale_shape.html'>scale_shape</a></span><span class="keyword">(</span><span class="symbol">...</span><span class="keyword">,</span> <span class="argument">solid</span> <span class="argument">=</span> <span class="number">TRUE</span><span class="keyword">)</span>

