<span class="functioncall"><a href='scale_shape.html'>scale_shape_continuous</a></span><span class="keyword">(</span><span class="symbol">...</span><span class="keyword">)</span></pre>
    
    <h2>Arguments</h2>
    <dl>
      <dt>solid</dt>
      <dd>Are the shapes solid, <code>TRUE</code>, or hollow
  <code>FALSE</code>?</dd>
      <dt>...</dt>
      <dd>common discrete scale parameters: <code>name</code>,
  <code>breaks</code>, <code>labels</code>, <code>na.value</code>,
  <code>limits</code> and <code>guide</code>.  See
  <code><a href='discrete_scale.html'>discrete_scale</a></code> for more details</dd>
    </dl>
    
    <div class="Description">
      <h2>Description</h2>
      
      <p>A continuous variable can not be mapped to shape.</p>
  
    </div>
    
